        </p>
        <p xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="Aink62">
          <l>intira viḻaviṟ pūvi ṉaṉṉa</l>
          <l>puṉṟalaip pēṭai variniḻa lakavu</l>
          <l>mivvūr maṅkaiyart tokuttiṉi</l>
          <l>yevvūr niṉṟaṉṟu makiḻnaniṉ ṟērē.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg xml:lang="en">


          <l> Like a flower at the Festival of Indra, </l>
          <l> your chariot attracts the girls of this village,</l>
          <l rend="indent4"> where the tawny-headed hen </l>
          <l rend="indent4"> keens in the dappled shade. </l>
          <l> In which village is your chariot parked now, o delightful man? </l>

        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
